mpic-level achievements\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2434}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cepelewicz:What was your initial goal?\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2493, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cepelewicz\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2465}, {\"ngram\": \"your initial goal\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ono:If you take the swimming out of it, we have Newton's laws of motion.\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2495, \"end\": 2498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yoko_Ono\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.676674061639069e-29, \"text\": \"Ono\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yoko_Ono\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yoko_Ono\"}, {\"begin\": 2543, \"end\": 2549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac_Newton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3173025569946855e-25, \"text\": \"Newton\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac_Newton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac_Newton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the swimming\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2523}, {\"ngram\": \"motion\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those are the equations that we work with.\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2610, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the equations\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We wanted to carefully understand the implications of Newton's laws applied to swimmers in the pool.\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2665, \"end\": 2671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac_Newton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3173025569946855e-25, \"text\": \"Newton\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac_Newton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac_Newton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the implications\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2661}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 2690, \"to\": 2698}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How do we measure acceleration, deceleration, and drag?\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2767, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"acceleration\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2742}, {\"ngram\": \"deceleration\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those were the first questions that we had to answer in the development of our tools.\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first questions\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2798}, {\"ngram\": \"the development\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2839}, {\"ngram\": \"our tools\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cepelewicz:How did you get started?\", \"from\": 2855, \"to\": 2890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ono:It began innocently enough-with Saran Wrap and accelerometers designed for shark tracking that I bought from marine-technology outfits.\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 3031, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2928, \"end\": 2938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saran_(plastic)\", \"score\": 0.9999999836054486, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Saran Wrap\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saran_(plastic)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saran_(plastic)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"accelerometers\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 2957}, {\"ngram\": \"shark tracking\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 2985}, {\"ngram\": \"marine-technology outfits\", \"from\": 3005, \"to\": 3030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We did not know what we were doing.\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3067, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I needed to fasten these accelerometers to swimmers.\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these accelerometers\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3107}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3119}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I got Saran Wrap and wrapped these sensors around their waists super tight.\", \"from\": 3121, \"to\": 3199, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Saran Wrap\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3140}, {\"ngram\": \"these sensors\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3166}, {\"ngram\": \"their waists\", \"from\": 3174, \"to\": 3186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some swimmers were just too powerful, so the sensors never stayed inside the Saran Wrap.\", \"from\": 3200, \"to\": 3288, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some swimmers\", \"from\": 3200, \"to\": 3213}, {\"ngram\": \"the sensors\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3252}, {\"ngram\": \"the Saran Wrap\", \"from\": 3273, \"to\": 3287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So now I have these belts that my wife made that have a little pocket for the sensors.\", \"from\": 3289, \"to\": 3375, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these belts\", \"from\": 3303, \"to\": 3314}, {\"ngram\": \"my wife\", \"from\": 3320, \"to\": 3327}, {\"ngram\": \"a little pocket\", \"from\": 3343, \"to\": 3358}, {\"ngram\": \"the sensors\", \"from\": 3363, \"to\": 3374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cepelewicz:It took time to get this experimental setup to work.\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3400}, {\"ngram\": \"this experimental setup\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ono:It was hard to even get the data.\", \"from\": 3442, \"to\": 3479, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the data\", \"from\": 3470, \"to\": 3478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our protocols for waterproofing were funny.\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3523, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our protocols\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3493}, {\"ngram\": \"waterproofing\", \"from\": 3498, \"to\": 3511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They looked like Boy Scout instructions: \\\"Wrap the accelerometer in tissue paper, burrito style.\\\"\", \"from\": 3524, \"to\": 3621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3545, \"end\": 3550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scouting\", \"score\": 0.9706247759056039, \"rank\": 0.03026417894730582, \"text\": \"Scout\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scouting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scouting\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the accelerometer\", \"from\": 3571, \"to\": 3588}, {\"ngram\": \"tissue paper\", \"from\": 3592, \"to\": 3604}, {\"ngram\": \"burrito style\", \"from\": 3606, \"to\": 3619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And we discovered that some of our sensors could fail.\", \"from\": 3622, \"to\": 3676, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our sensors\", \"from\": 3653, \"to\": 3664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were very sensitive to light.\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"light\", \"from\": 3705, \"to\": 3710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So we had to fashion little plastic UV covers to protect them.\", \"from\": 3712, \"to\": 3774, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"little plastic UV covers\", \"from\": 3733, \"to\": 3757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It wasn't that long ago that we were that amateur.\", \"from\": 3776, \"to\": 3826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that amateur\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have come a long way since then.\", \"from\": 3827, \"to\": 3862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cepelewicz:What kind of data do you collect?\", \"from\": 3864, \"to\": 3908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cepelewicz\", \"from\": 3864, \"to\": 3874}, {\"ngram\": \"What kind\", \"from\": 3875, \"to\": 3884}, {\"ngram\": \"data\", \"from\": 3888, \"to\": 3892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ono:I record swims with high-definition video, and with accelerometers and force paddles.\", \"from\": 3910, \"to\": 3999, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"high-definition video\", \"from\": 3934, \"to\": 3955}, {\"ngram\": \"accelerometers\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 3980}, {\"ngram\": \"paddles\", \"from\": 3991, \"to\": 3998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have also assembled a very large battery of tests that look nothing like swimming.\", \"from\": 4000, \"to\": 4084, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very large battery\", \"from\": 4022, \"to\": 4042}, {\"ngram\": \"tests\", \"from\": 4046, \"to\": 4051}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 4062, \"to\": 4069}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 4075, \"to\": 4083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I test how athletes swim when they take their kicks at different tempos.\", \"from\": 4085, \"to\": 4157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 4096, \"to\": 4104}, {\"ngram\": \"their kicks\", \"from\": 4125, \"to\": 4136}, {\"ngram\": \"different tempos\", \"from\": 4140, \"to\": 4156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I test how flexible they are, how tired they get after certain tasks.\", \"from\": 4158, \"to\": 4227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"certain tasks\", \"from\": 4213, \"to\": 4226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to get a good sense of what their capabilities will be.\", \"from\": 4228, \"to\": 4290, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good sense\", \"from\": 4242, \"to\": 4254}, {\"ngram\": \"their capabilities\", \"from\": 4263, \"to\": 4281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During these swims and tests, I measure the force that is generated in three-dimensional space by the athlete's legs, by undulation at the hips, and by their hands.\", \"from\": 4292, \"to\": 4456, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these swims\", \"from\": 4299, \"to\": 4310}, {\"ngram\": \"tests\", \"from\": 4315, \"to\": 4320}, {\"ngram\": \"the force\", \"from\": 4332, \"to\": 4341}, {\"ngram\": \"three-dimensional space\", \"from\": 4363, \"to\": 4386}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete's legs\", \"from\": 4390, \"to\": 4408}, {\"ngram\": \"undulation\", \"from\": 4413, \"to\": 4423}, {\"ngram\": \"the hips\", \"from\": 4427, \"to\": 4435}, {\"ngram\": \"their hands\", \"from\": 4444, \"to\": 4455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"High-definition video generally captures only 24 screenshots per second.\", \"from\": 4457, \"to\": 4529, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"High-definition video\", \"from\": 4457, \"to\": 4478}, {\"ngram\": \"only 24 screenshots\", \"from\": 4498, \"to\": 4517}, {\"ngram\": \"second\", \"from\": 4522, \"to\": 4528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each sensor gives me 512 force vectors per second.\", \"from\": 4530, \"to\": 4580, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Each sensor\", \"from\": 4530, \"to\": 4541}, {\"ngram\": \"512 force vectors\", \"from\": 4551, \"to\": 4568}, {\"ngram\": \"second\", \"from\": 4573, \"to\": 4579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They can reveal things you will never see in the video.\", \"from\": 4581, \"to\": 4636, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 4597, \"to\": 4603}, {\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 4626, \"to\": 4635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cepelewicz:Like what?\", \"from\": 4638, \"to\": 4659, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cepelewicz\", \"from\": 4638, \"to\": 4648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ono:One subtle thing that we picked up on very easily-and you would not see it with your eyes-is how an athlete might change the execution of their kicks three strokes away from the wall, causing them to lose time.\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4661, \"end\": 4664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yoko_Ono\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.676674061639069e-29, \"text\": \"Ono\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yoko_Ono\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yoko_Ono\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One subtle thing\", \"from\": 4665, \"to\": 4681}, {\"ngram\": \"your eyes\", \"from\": 4745, \"to\": 4754}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 4762, \"to\": 4772}, {\"ngram\": \"the execution\", \"from\": 4786, \"to\": 4799}, {\"ngram\": \"their kicks\", \"from\": 4803, \"to\": 4814}, {\"ngram\": \"the wall\", \"from\": 4839, \"to\": 4847}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4870, \"to\": 4874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's just one example.\", \"from\": 4877, \"to\": 4901, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just one example\", \"from\": 4884, \"to\": 4900}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Using our data, we perform a very careful and serious analysis of each individual swimmer.\", \"from\": 4902, \"to\": 4992, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our data\", \"from\": 4908, \"to\": 4916}, {\"ngram\": \"a very careful and serious analysis\", \"from\": 4929, \"to\": 4964}, {\"ngram\": \"each individual swimmer\", \"from\": 4968, \"to\": 4991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We get a breakdown of the swim.\", \"from\": 4993, \"to\": 5024, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a breakdown\", \"from\": 5000, \"to\": 5011}, {\"ngram\": \"the swim\", \"from\": 5015, \"to\": 5023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My first tests look for where you are decelerating for no good reason.\", \"from\": 5025, \"to\": 5095, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My first tests\", \"from\": 5025, \"to\": 5039}, {\"ngram\": \"no good reason\", \"from\": 5080, \"to\": 5094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some athletes really struggle with their transitions, coming into and coming out of a wall.\", \"from\": 5096, \"to\": 5187, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some athletes\", \"from\": 5096, \"to\": 5109}, {\"ngram\": \"their transitions\", \"from\": 5131, \"to\": 5148}, {\"ngram\": \"a wall\", \"from\": 5180, \"to\": 5186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or they might need to correct their head placement in a streamline, an underwater glide where they are not actually swimming.\", \"from\": 5188, \"to\": 5313, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their head placement\", \"from\": 5218, \"to\": 5238}, {\"ngram\": \"a streamline\", \"from\": 5242, \"to\": 5254}, {\"ngram\": \"an underwater glide\", \"from\": 5256, \"to\": 5275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Olympic and World Championship level, where races might come down to hundredths of a second, these things matter.\", \"from\": 5314, \"to\": 5434, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic and World Championship level\", \"from\": 5317, \"to\": 5357}, {\"ngram\": \"races\", \"from\": 5365, \"to\": 5370}, {\"ngram\": \"hundredths\", \"from\": 5390, \"to\": 5400}, {\"ngram\": \"these things\", \"from\": 5414, \"to\": 5426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once we wipe out those sources of deceleration, then we look at what limbs are doing in motion.\", \"from\": 5436, \"to\": 5531, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those sources\", \"from\": 5453, \"to\": 5466}, {\"ngram\": \"deceleration\", \"from\": 5470, \"to\": 5482}, {\"ngram\": \"limbs\", \"from\": 5505, \"to\": 5510}, {\"ngram\": \"motion\", \"from\": 5524, \"to\": 5530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As you fatigue, how is your stroke falling apart?\", \"from\": 5532, \"to\": 5581, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your stroke\", \"from\": 5555, \"to\": 5566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Are you maximizing the percentage of force you generate so that your body swims in the right direction?\", \"from\": 5582, \"to\": 5685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the percentage\", \"from\": 5601, \"to\": 5615}, {\"ngram\": \"force\", \"from\": 5619, \"to\": 5624}, {\"ngram\": \"your body\", \"from\": 5646, \"to\": 5655}, {\"ngram\": \"the right direction\", \"from\": 5665, \"to\": 5684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read: The glorious drama of the U.S. swim team Cepelewicz:How do you extract this information from your data?\", \"from\": 5687, \"to\": 5797, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Read\", \"from\": 5687, \"to\": 5691}, {\"ngram\": \"The glorious drama\", \"from\": 5693, \"to\": 5711}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. swim team\", \"from\": 5715, \"to\": 5733}, {\"ngram\": \"Cepelewicz\", \"from\": 5734, \"to\": 5744}, {\"ngram\": \"this information\", \"from\": 5764, \"to\": 5780}, {\"ngram\": \"your data\", \"from\": 5786, \"to\": 5795}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ono:Some of it is as simple as linear algebra.\", \"from\": 5799, \"to\": 5845, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"linear algebra\", \"from\": 5830, \"to\": 5844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When an athlete takes a stroke, they are generating force that can be pointed downward, upward, to the right or to the left, or in the direction of the swim.\", \"from\": 5846, \"to\": 6003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 5851, \"to\": 5861}, {\"ngram\": \"a stroke\", \"from\": 5868, \"to\": 5876}, {\"ngram\": \"force\", \"from\": 5898, \"to\": 5903}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 5945, \"to\": 5954}, {\"ngram\": \"the direction\", \"from\": 5977, \"to\": 5990}, {\"ngram\": \"the swim\", \"from\": 5994, \"to\": 6002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use linear-algebra techniques to calculate the percentage in each of those directions.\", \"from\": 6004, \"to\": 6093, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"linear-algebra techniques\", \"from\": 6011, \"to\": 6036}, {\"ngram\": \"the percentage\", \"from\": 6050, \"to\": 6064}, {\"ngram\": \"those directions\", \"from\": 6076, \"to\": 6092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Would you believe that we have never measured anyone who was more than 60 percent efficient in the four strokes -freestyle, breaststroke, butterfly, and backstroke?\", \"from\": 6095, \"to\": 6259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 6141, \"to\": 6147}, {\"ngram\": \"the four strokes -freestyle\", \"from\": 6190, \"to\": 6217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's basically impossible.\", \"from\": 6260, \"to\": 6286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In April, we had Paige Madden wear force sensors, and we modeled the path of her hand as she took a stroke and recovered.\", \"from\": 6287, \"to\": 6408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6304, \"end\": 6316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paige_Madden\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paige Madden\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paige_Madden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paige_Madden\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 6290, \"to\": 6295}, {\"ngram\": \"force sensors\", \"from\": 6322, \"to\": 6335}, {\"ngram\": \"the path\", \"from\": 6352, \"to\": 6360}, {\"ngram\": \"her hand\", \"from\": 6364, \"to\": 6372}, {\"ngram\": \"a stroke\", \"from\": 6385, \"to\": 6393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We computed that in the first lap of her swim, 59.1 percent of the force her right hand generated was propelling her in the direction she wanted to go.\", \"from\": 6409, \"to\": 6560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first lap\", \"from\": 6429, \"to\": 6442}, {\"ngram\": \"her swim\", \"from\": 6446, \"to\": 6454}, {\"ngram\": \"59.1 percent\", \"from\": 6456, \"to\": 6468}, {\"ngram\": \"the force\", \"from\": 6472, \"to\": 6481}, {\"ngram\": \"her right hand\", \"from\": 6482, \"to\": 6496}, {\"ngram\": \"the direction\", \"from\": 6529, \"to\": 6542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is awesome.\", \"from\": 6561, \"to\": 6577, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But by Lap 8, only 42.1 percent was propelling her forward.\", \"from\": 6579, \"to\": 6638, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lap\", \"from\": 6586, \"to\": 6589}, {\"ngram\": \"only 42.1 percent\", \"from\": 6593, \"to\": 6610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only was she getting more tired, but her execution was starting to fall apart.\", \"from\": 6639, \"to\": 6721, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her execution\", \"from\": 6680, \"to\": 6693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So using just these insights from linear algebra, we gave her some cues about how to swim the race differently.\", \"from\": 6722, \"to\": 6833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6756, \"end\": 6770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linear_algebra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.166087084545929e-27, \"text\": \"linear algebra\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linear_algebra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linear_algebra\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just these insights\", \"from\": 6731, \"to\": 6750}, {\"ngram\": \"some cues\", \"from\": 6784, \"to\": 6793}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 6812, \"to\": 6820}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the next day, on Lap 8, she was close to 50 percent.\", \"from\": 6834, \"to\": 6890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lap\", \"from\": 6855, \"to\": 6858}, {\"ngram\": \"close to 50 percent\", \"from\": 6870, \"to\": 6889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One month later, she swam her personal best.\", \"from\": 6891, \"to\": 6935, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our paddles do not let you lie.\", \"from\": 6937, \"to\": 6968, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our paddles\", \"from\": 6937, \"to\": 6948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We do not let you fool yourselves.\", \"from\": 6969, \"to\": 7003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cepelewicz:And this math works the same for all four strokes?\", \"from\": 7005, \"to\": 7066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cepelewicz\", \"from\": 7005, \"to\": 7015}, {\"ngram\": \"this math\", \"from\": 7020, \"to\": 7029}, {\"ngram\": \"all four strokes\", \"from\": 7049, \"to\": 7065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ono:I have never been able to get our force sensors to work for breaststroke.\", \"from\": 7068, \"to\": 7145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our force\", \"from\": 7102, \"to\": 7111}, {\"ngram\": \"breaststroke\", \"from\": 7132, \"to\": 7144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is too much going on.\", \"from\": 7146, \"to\": 7173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I get data, but I can not make heads or tails out of it.\", \"from\": 7174, \"to\": 7230, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"data\", \"from\": 7180, \"to\": 7184}, {\"ngram\": \"heads\", \"from\": 7205, \"to\": 7210}, {\"ngram\": \"tails\", \"from\": 7214, \"to\": 7219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cepelewicz:Why is breaststroke harder to deal with?\", \"from\": 7232, \"to\": 7283, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ono:I wish I could tell you.\", \"from\": 7285, \"to\": 7313, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean, in breaststroke, your hands are doing much more in terms of in-sweep, out-sweep.\", \"from\": 7314, \"to\": 7402, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"breaststroke\", \"from\": 7325, \"to\": 7337}, {\"ngram\": \"your hands\", \"from\": 7339, \"to\": 7349}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 7373, \"to\": 7378}, {\"ngram\": \"in-sweep, out-sweep\", \"from\": 7382, \"to\": 7401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's a hard problem.\", \"from\": 7403, \"to\": 7425, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hard problem\", \"from\": 7410, \"to\": 7424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I do not know.\", \"from\": 7426, \"to\": 7444, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cepelewicz:You also use your data to make predictions and develop race strategies, right?\", \"from\": 7446, \"to\": 7535, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your data\", \"from\": 7470, \"to\": 7479}, {\"ngram\": \"predictions\", \"from\": 7488, \"to\": 7499}, {\"ngram\": \"race strategies\", \"from\": 7512, \"to\": 7527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ono:That's right.\", \"from\": 7537, \"to\": 7554, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We can use all our data to build a \\\"digital twin\\\" of an athlete.\", \"from\": 7555, \"to\": 7619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all our data\", \"from\": 7566, \"to\": 7578}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"digital twin\", \"from\": 7588, \"to\": 7603}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 7608, \"to\": 7618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Digital twins are mathematical models of complicated systems and processes, such as the spread of COVID or the migration of populations of animals-things that vary over time.\", \"from\": 7620, \"to\": 7794, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7620, \"end\": 7633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_twin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Digital twins\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_twin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Digital_twin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mathematical models\", \"from\": 7638, \"to\": 7657}, {\"ngram\": \"complicated systems\", \"from\": 7661, \"to\": 7680}, {\"ngram\": \"processes\", \"from\": 7685, \"to\": 7694}, {\"ngram\": \"the spread\", \"from\": 7704, \"to\": 7714}, {\"ngram\": \"COVID\", \"from\": 7718, \"to\": 7723}, {\"ngram\": \"the migration\", \"from\": 7727, \"to\": 7740}, {\"ngram\": \"populations\", \"from\": 7744, \"to\": 7755}, {\"ngram\": \"animals-things\", \"from\": 7759, \"to\": 7773}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 7789, \"to\": 7793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Except, in my case, it really is a digital twin.\", \"from\": 7796, \"to\": 7844, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my case\", \"from\": 7807, \"to\": 7814}, {\"ngram\": \"a digital twin\", \"from\": 7829, \"to\": 7843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It looks like an EKG, goingtch, tch, tch, and it's developed based on the data I have captured about an athlete's movements.\", \"from\": 7845, \"to\": 7969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7862, \"end\": 7865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electrocardiography\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"EKG\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electrocardiography\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electrocardiography\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"goingtch\", \"from\": 7867, \"to\": 7875}, {\"ngram\": \"tch\", \"from\": 7877, \"to\": 7880}, {\"ngram\": \"tch\", \"from\": 7882, \"to\": 7885}, {\"ngram\": \"the data\", \"from\": 7915, \"to\": 7923}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete's movements\", \"from\": 7946, \"to\": 7968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can model how they will race under different conditions.\", \"from\": 7970, \"to\": 8028, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"different conditions\", \"from\": 8007, \"to\": 8027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the last seven or eight years, I have collected thousands of swims from more than 100 top athletes.\", \"from\": 8029, \"to\": 8133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last seven or eight years\", \"from\": 8034, \"to\": 8063}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 8082, \"to\": 8091}, {\"ngram\": \"swims\", \"from\": 8095, \"to\": 8100}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 100 top athletes\", \"from\": 8106, \"to\": 8132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I can race your digital twin against the database, make adjustments, and assemble the optimal formula you should use for your race-how many kicks do you take off the dive; where do you place your hands coming into a turn; how many breaths do you take, and in what pattern?\", \"from\": 8134, \"to\": 8409, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your digital twin\", \"from\": 8148, \"to\": 8165}, {\"ngram\": \"the database\", \"from\": 8174, \"to\": 8186}, {\"ngram\": \"adjustments\", \"from\": 8193, \"to\": 8204}, {\"ngram\": \"the optimal formula\", \"from\": 8219, \"to\": 8238}, {\"ngram\": \"your race\", \"from\": 8258, \"to\": 8267}, {\"ngram\": \"how many kicks\", \"from\": 8268, \"to\": 8282}, {\"ngram\": \"the dive\", \"from\": 8299, \"to\": 8307}, {\"ngram\": \"your hands\", \"from\": 8328, \"to\": 8338}, {\"ngram\": \"a turn\", \"from\": 8351, \"to\": 8357}, {\"ngram\": \"how many breaths\", \"from\": 8359, \"to\": 8375}, {\"ngram\": \"what pattern\", \"from\": 8396, \"to\": 8408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's curated per athlete, per inch.\", \"from\": 8410, \"to\": 8445, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athlete\", \"from\": 8427, \"to\": 8434}, {\"ngram\": \"inch\", \"from\": 8440, \"to\": 8444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can say: If you swim using this formula, you are going to do the 100-yard backstroke in under 48 seconds.\", \"from\": 8446, \"to\": 8554, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this formula\", \"from\": 8476, \"to\": 8488}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100-yard backstroke\", \"from\": 8510, \"to\": 8533}, {\"ngram\": \"48 seconds\", \"from\": 8543, \"to\": 8553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These simulated races between digital twins might show a competitor two or three feet ahead of you at a particular point in time-but I do not want you to worry about that, because you will see that in Leg 3, they are going to slow down, and you will catch up.\", \"from\": 8556, \"to\": 8815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These simulated races\", \"from\": 8556, \"to\": 8577}, {\"ngram\": \"digital twins\", \"from\": 8586, \"to\": 8599}, {\"ngram\": \"a competitor\", \"from\": 8611, \"to\": 8623}, {\"ngram\": \"a particular point\", \"from\": 8658, \"to\": 8676}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 8680, \"to\": 8684}, {\"ngram\": \"Leg\", \"from\": 8757, \"to\": 8760}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you watch footage of NCAA races, you will probably get a sense that the UVA athletes seem to have this extra swagger, like they cannot lose.\", \"from\": 8817, \"to\": 8960, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8841, \"end\": 8845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.999999551136271, \"rank\": 4.4886303236760234e-07, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 8892, \"end\": 8895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultraviolet\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.894651372532708e-12, \"text\": \"UVA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultraviolet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultraviolet\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"footage\", \"from\": 8830, \"to\": 8837}, {\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 8875, \"to\": 8882}, {\"ngram\": \"this extra swagger\", \"from\": 8918, \"to\": 8936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And there is of course truth to that, because they are winning all the time.\", \"from\": 8961, \"to\": 9037, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 8977, \"to\": 8983}, {\"ngram\": \"truth\", \"from\": 8984, \"to\": 8989}, {\"ngram\": \"all the time\", \"from\": 9024, \"to\": 9036}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But one of the unexpected benefits of our work is, in their mind, they think,If I swim that formula, I win the race.\", \"from\": 9038, \"to\": 9154, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the unexpected benefits\", \"from\": 9049, \"to\": 9072}, {\"ngram\": \"our work\", \"from\": 9076, \"to\": 9084}, {\"ngram\": \"their mind\", \"from\": 9092, \"to\": 9102}, {\"ngram\": \"that formula\", \"from\": 9125, \"to\": 9137}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 9145, \"to\": 9153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cepelewicz:What challenges have you had to overcome while doing these analyses?\", \"from\": 9156, \"to\": 9235, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"What challenges\", \"from\": 9167, \"to\": 9182}, {\"ngram\": \"these analyses\", \"from\": 9220, \"to\": 9234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ono:There are several.\", \"from\": 9237, \"to\": 9259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, the question of orientation in three-dimensional space is critical.\", \"from\": 9260, \"to\": 9340, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 9264, \"to\": 9271}, {\"ngram\": \"the question\", \"from\": 9273, \"to\": 9285}, {\"ngram\": \"orientation\", \"from\": 9289, \"to\": 9300}, {\"ngram\": \"three-dimensional space\", \"from\": 9304, \"to\": 9327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your body is constantly in motion.\", \"from\": 9341, \"to\": 9375, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your body\", \"from\": 9341, \"to\": 9350}, {\"ngram\": \"motion\", \"from\": 9368, \"to\": 9374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So how do we decide when the force is actually going in the direction of the swim?\", \"from\": 9376, \"to\": 9458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the force\", \"from\": 9401, \"to\": 9410}, {\"ngram\": \"the direction\", \"from\": 9432, \"to\": 9445}, {\"ngram\": \"the swim\", \"from\": 9449, \"to\": 9457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not that easy.\", \"from\": 9459, \"to\": 9478, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We had to make sure that we were basing our analyses on the right orientations.\", \"from\": 9479, \"to\": 9558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our analyses\", \"from\": 9519, \"to\": 9531}, {\"ngram\": \"the right orientations\", \"from\": 9535, \"to\": 9557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Accelerometer data is very noisy.\", \"from\": 9560, \"to\": 9593, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Accelerometer data\", \"from\": 9560, \"to\": 9578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Accelerometers are very sensitive.\", \"from\": 9594, \"to\": 9628, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Accelerometers\", \"from\": 9594, \"to\": 9608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So some of the mathematics that's deeply theoretical involves how you smooth the data to dampen out the noise.\", \"from\": 9629, \"to\": 9739, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mathematics\", \"from\": 9640, \"to\": 9655}, {\"ngram\": \"the data\", \"from\": 9706, \"to\": 9714}, {\"ngram\": \"the noise\", \"from\": 9729, \"to\": 9738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I need to know when a peak is meaningful.\", \"from\": 9740, \"to\": 9781, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a peak\", \"from\": 9760, \"to\": 9766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have to be able to look at a stream of accelerometer data and say: This is where you are breathing to the right, but you lifted your head up a little too much, or this is how much force you generated in the instant you moved off the wall, before you started decelerating.\", \"from\": 9782, \"to\": 10055, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a stream\", \"from\": 9811, \"to\": 9819}, {\"ngram\": \"accelerometer data\", \"from\": 9823, \"to\": 9841}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 9886, \"to\": 9895}, {\"ngram\": \"your head\", \"from\": 9912, \"to\": 9921}, {\"ngram\": \"how much force\", \"from\": 9955, \"to\": 9969}, {\"ngram\": \"the instant\", \"from\": 9987, \"to\": 9998}, {\"ngram\": \"the wall\", \"from\": 10013, \"to\": 10021}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I need that level of sensitivity.\", \"from\": 10056, \"to\": 10089, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that level\", \"from\": 10063, \"to\": 10073}, {\"ngram\": \"sensitivity\", \"from\": 10077, \"to\": 10088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I need to have confidence that the numbers I get mean what I think they mean.\", \"from\": 10090, \"to\": 10167, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 10105, \"to\": 10115}, {\"ngram\": \"the numbers\", \"from\": 10121, \"to\": 10132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Figuring out the correct method to smooth out this noisy data was probably the most sophisticated type of mathematics that we had to do, and that's very secret.\", \"from\": 10169, \"to\": 10329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the correct method\", \"from\": 10182, \"to\": 10200}, {\"ngram\": \"this noisy data\", \"from\": 10215, \"to\": 10230}, {\"ngram\": \"the most sophisticated type\", \"from\": 10244, \"to\": 10271}, {\"ngram\": \"mathematics\", \"from\": 10275, \"to\": 10286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read: What about the math Olympians?\", \"from\": 10331, \"to\": 10367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Read\", \"from\": 10331, \"to\": 10335}, {\"ngram\": \"the math Olympians\", \"from\": 10348, \"to\": 10366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cepelewicz:What have you taken away from this experience?\", \"from\": 10369, \"to\": 10426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cepelewicz\", \"from\": 10369, \"to\": 10379}, {\"ngram\": \"this experience\", \"from\": 10410, \"to\": 10425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ono:We have not discovered or invented any new math.\", \"from\": 10428, \"to\": 10480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any new math\", \"from\": 10467, \"to\": 10479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are not doing rocket science here.\", \"from\": 10481, \"to\": 10518, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rocket science\", \"from\": 10498, \"to\": 10512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What I think this proves is that the attention to detail that comes from thinking analytically has merit.\", \"from\": 10519, \"to\": 10624, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the attention\", \"from\": 10552, \"to\": 10565}, {\"ngram\": \"detail\", \"from\": 10569, \"to\": 10575}, {\"ngram\": \"thinking\", \"from\": 10592, \"to\": 10600}, {\"ngram\": \"merit\", \"from\": 10618, \"to\": 10623}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to find the stuff no one else has, and use Newton's laws, together with experimentation and some linear algebra, to help craft the best performances for the athletes we work with.\", \"from\": 10625, \"to\": 10811, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10675, \"end\": 10681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac_Newton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3173025569946855e-25, \"text\": \"Newton\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac_Newton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac_Newton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the stuff\", \"from\": 10640, \"to\": 10649}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 10650, \"to\": 10656}, {\"ngram\": \"experimentation\", \"from\": 10704, \"to\": 10719}, {\"ngram\": \"some linear algebra\", \"from\": 10724, \"to\": 10743}, {\"ngram\": \"the best performances\", \"from\": 10759, \"to\": 10780}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 10785, \"to\": 10797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are still coaches that do not take us seriously.\", \"from\": 10813, \"to\": 10867, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 10829, \"to\": 10836}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 10854, \"to\": 10856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that's not my job.\", \"from\": 10868, \"to\": 10890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my job\", \"from\": 10883, \"to\": 10889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My job is to help these athletes improve as swimmers, and to help get as many of them on the Olympic team as we can.\", \"from\": 10891, \"to\": 11007, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My job\", \"from\": 10891, \"to\": 10897}, {\"ngram\": \"these athletes\", \"from\": 10909, \"to\": 10923}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 10935, \"to\": 10943}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic team\", \"from\": 10980, \"to\": 10996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a pure mathematician by training.\", \"from\": 11009, \"to\": 11047, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pure mathematician\", \"from\": 11014, \"to\": 11034}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 11038, \"to\": 11046}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That can be rather lonely.\", \"from\": 11048, \"to\": 11074, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So this is perhaps the one time in my life where my training as a mathematical scientist seems to matter to a large group of people.\", \"from\": 11075, \"to\": 11207, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the one time\", \"from\": 11094, \"to\": 11106}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 11110, \"to\": 11117}, {\"ngram\": \"my training\", \"from\": 11124, \"to\": 11135}, {\"ngram\": \"a mathematical scientist\", \"from\": 11139, \"to\": 11163}, {\"ngram\": \"a large group\", \"from\": 11183, \"to\": 11196}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 11200, \"to\": 11206}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been a dream ride.\", \"from\": 11208, \"to\": 11233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a dream ride\", \"from\": 11220, \"to\": 11232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheAtlantic.com \\u00a92026The Atlantic Monthly Group.\", \"from\": 11235, \"to\": 11283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11260, \"end\": 11276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Atlantic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Atlantic Monthly\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Atlantic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Atlantic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 11284, \"to\": 11304, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and the GooglePrivacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply\", \"from\": 11306, \"to\": 11394, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This site\", \"from\": 11306, \"to\": 11315}, {\"ngram\": \"reCAPTCHA\", \"from\": 11332, \"to\": 11341}, {\"ngram\": \"the GooglePrivacy PolicyandTerms\", \"from\": 11346, \"to\": 11378}, {\"ngram\": \"Serviceapply\", \"from\": 11382, \"to\": 11394}]}]}"